00:18:06,710 --> 00:18:07,810
Oh.

307
00:18:07,810 --> 00:18:08,920
Yes.

308
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,930
We've met quite a lot.

309
00:18:10,930 --> 00:18:12,560
In Japan, too.

310
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:16,430
