345
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:31,820
You can't even own up to me, either.

346
00:20:31,820 --> 00:20:32,680
What?

347
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,430
Even you...

348
00:20:34,430 --> 00:20:37,420
can't tell anyone about me.

349
00:20:38,270 --> 00:20:40,840
