365
00:21:31,740 --> 00:21:33,940
I'll be going.

366
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:35,600
Bye.

367
00:21:49,660 --> 00:21:52,490
He doesn't even know...

368
00:21:59,770 --> 00:22:00,850
Mister.

369
00:22:00,850 --> 00:22:02,560
