423
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:03,470
That way, Inhyung can do something.

424
00:26:03,470 --> 00:26:04,820
Right?

425
00:26:09,900 --> 00:26:12,310
This prick.

426
00:26:58,420 --> 00:27:00,670
 The door is unlocked. 

427
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:16,300
