459
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:44,340
ended up protecting no one.

460
00:29:46,230 --> 00:29:48,340
It hurt everyone.

461
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:53,300
And it's my fault.

462
00:29:54,180 --> 00:29:55,630
So...

463
00:29:55,630 --> 00:29:58,090
