467
00:30:12,170 --> 00:30:15,420
You know I can't do much.

468
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:44,450
You're awake?

469
00:30:44,450 --> 00:30:45,330
You're here.

470
00:30:45,330 --> 00:30:47,900
It's macchiato today.

471
00:30:50,190 --> 00:30:52,830
