526
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:42,120
Huh?

527
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:45,870
It's not like that.

528
00:33:45,870 --> 00:33:50,650
But as for me... I don't really know.

529
00:33:50,650 --> 00:33:53,750
About you three.

530
00:33:58,040 --> 00:34:01,590
